com.google.crypto.tink.integration.gcpkms

Class GcpKmsAead.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.crypto.tink.integration.gcpkms.GcpKmsAead.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    GcpKmsAead

    public static final class GcpKmsAead.Builder
extends Object
    A Builder to create an Aead backed by GCP Cloud KMS.

    If setKeyManagementServiceClient(com.google.cloud.kms.v1.KeyManagementServiceClient) is used, the Aead will communicate with Cloud KMS via gRPC given a KeyManagementServiceClient instance. If setCloudKms(com.google.api.services.cloudkms.v1.CloudKMS) is used, the Aead will communicate with Cloud KMS via HTTP given a CloudKMS instance.

    For new users we recommend using setKeyManagementServiceClient(com.google.cloud.kms.v1.KeyManagementServiceClient).
